pageProduct.name: Swisse Beauty Collagen Detox 120g
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Swisse Beauty Collagen Detox is a premium quality formula to support collagen formation, skin health and skin repair, and assist the natural liver detoxification process.

This convenient, great tasting powder is specially formulated with:

Vitamin C to support collagen formation, skin repair and skin elasticity.
Collagen peptides from type I and III collagen - collagen is a major protein found in connective tissues and important for the skin’s matrix.
Zinc to maintain healthy skin.
Milk thistle, traditionally used in Western herbal medicine to assist the body’s natural detoxification processes and maintain healthy liver function.
Great tasting natural pineapple flavour.

Size: 120g

Flavour: Pineapple

Warnings

WARNINGS:

Vitamin & mineral supplements should not replace a balanced diet. If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional.

Ingredients

Each scoop (6 g) contains:

COLLAGEN Hydrolysed Collagen 625mg
MILK THISTLE (Silybum marianum extract 42.90 mg) equiv. dry fruit 3g
VITAMIN C (ascorbic acid) 83.30mg
NICOTINAMIDE 5mg
ZINC (from zinc citrate dehydrate) 5 mg
GREEN TEA (Camellia sinensis extract 6 mg) equiv. Dry leaf (standardised to contain caffeine 1.8 mg) 900mg
Spearmint oil (Mentha spicata dry leaf powder) 50mg
GINGER (Zingiber officinale extract 10 mg) equiv. Dry rhizome 50mg
Acacia 250mg
Contains sucralose & sulfites

Directions

ADULT DOSAGE:

Using the enclosed scoop, mix one level scoop (6 g) with 250 ml of water or juice.

Consume once daily, during or immediately after a meal, or as directed by a healthcare professional.

Some settling of the powder may occur after mixing.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

STORAGE:

Store below 25°C in a cool, dry place. Do not use if cap seal is broken.
